name: [Umi AI] Elden Ring-Style Ghosts and Gods by DutchAlex
description:
Have you ever heard of Angelarium? It's a website with a specific, highly mythological art style that truly captures the mind and seizes one's imagination. Now, you can mimic this art style using DutchAlex's awesome new Locon Lora.

This Lora does not require any specific trigger words. Simply make sure to add 'No Humans' to get that ancient, Doom Eternal-esque Cyber/Techno-Angel vibe in your images.

This lora has been tested on and works best with the Umi AI models, in particular the Macross Ultimate and Olympus Landscape models. It also works well with Aphrodite for realistic-looking gens.

modelVersions.name: Angelarium v1
trainedWords: no trigger words necessary, just include 'no humans' to achieve the ideal styling.
